    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "I am in receipt of your letter dated",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "February 1, 1959. In response to your request, I",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "wish to advise that information in the files of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "the Federal Bureau of Investigation is confidential",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "and available for official use only. I know you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "will understand the reason for this rule and will",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "not infer either that we do or that we do not have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "the data you desire.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "I am at liberty, however, to advise that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "the investigation of unidentified flying objects",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "is not within the jurisdiction of this Bureau. This",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "matter is of primary interest to the Department of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "the Air Force and, accordingly, I am sending a copy",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "of your letter to the Director of Special Investigations,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "The Inspector General, Department of the Air Force,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "Building Tempo E, 4th and Adams Drive, S. W.,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Washington, D. C., to whom you may desire to direct",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "further inquiries in this matter.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
